{"tid":2058613,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"楊潤雄致函中小學校長：不應容許任何罷課　叫口號、拉人鏈應勸止","createTime":"2020-06-10T09:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T10:35:32.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"01bfd30c80f91ebbf231d2f337b0cc42e8f3f4ba","tid":2058613,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:56:40.000Z","msg":"由多個工會組成的「二百萬三罷聯合陣線」及「中學生行動籌備平台」針對港版國安法，計劃於下周日（14日）將舉行「罷工罷課公投」。<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄今日（10日）去信全港中小學校長，要求學校向學生解釋國安法不影響港人權利及自由，又指學校不應任由學生參加「這些毫無意義的『公投』活動，更不應容許任何模式的罷課」，若校內有人叫口號、拉人鏈、唱帶政治訊息歌曲、貼帶政治訊息標語或罷課，學校應勸止，否則應予以懲處。<br />\n<br />\n而老師罷教非「重要緊急的私人事務」，不可請特別有薪假，若有教師參與罷課即屬疏忽職守、將政治帶入校園，學校應採紀律行動，強調教育局會嚴肅跟進。"},{"pid":"e6faa42f0fe398690b7df84db79e3438244fa543","tid":2058613,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:57:29.000Z","msg":"應該打999拉晒班學生啦，你話係咪呀楊局長"},{"pid":"1ce7daa13b149019d608aca9183ea298dae90767","tid":2058613,"uid":83344,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:00:12.000Z","msg":"咁喺學校舉行支持國安法集會，派傳單得唔得"},{"pid":"e4a55d7f65dbe8a3aff40063a7ceb69bd706ef96","tid":2058613,"uid":98139,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜撚都唔比做"},{"pid":"682ee1ab3d4c0025802e53d61c4b806fa7d08a65","tid":2058613,"uid":321059,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:01:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">要求學校向學生解釋國安法不影響港人權利及自由</span><br />\n<br />\n咁算唔算將政治帶入校園？"},{"pid":"eee083678764b2768e9cdd0fe4190b7481d26737","tid":2058613,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學校唔比做咪係條街做，而且學校做你吹得我脹"},{"pid":"91c0ac51bb9c7bd52de70bfb76202611cd48d698","tid":2058613,"uid":83228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:05:04.000Z","msg":"咁人鏈罷課 支持國安法<br />\n會點？"},{"pid":"793032c9eb3dbcb386ff5a5367a86054f8fb19e2","tid":2058613,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:12:31.000Z","msg":"插手亂搞教育嘅一定死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79098fc911fb43dc3f065a2ed016e1fe096fec17","tid":2058613,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"682ee1ab3d4c0025802e53d61c4b806fa7d08a65","tid":2058613,"uid":321059,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:01:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">要求學校向學生解釋國安法不影響港人權利及自由</span><br />\n<br />\n咁算唔算將政治帶入校園？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:34:24.000Z","msg":"根本就係自己整埋fake news"},{"pid":"4c670be3a3d1a55e4aacb78f495298645b991466","tid":2058613,"uid":59633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eee083678764b2768e9cdd0fe4190b7481d26737","tid":2058613,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學校唔比做咪係條街做，而且學校做你吹得我脹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:35:32.000Z","msg":"有d學校係校外一路行一路食早餐都話係犯校規<br />\n唔係話係條街做就唔會理<br />\n學校打壓起上來可以痴線過社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}